Prefix Sum is a type of algorithm that helps to keep track the sum of elements to the current position
Kadanes algorithm: This algorithm help us to find the maximum sum so far while keep tracking the current sum
The pseudo code of the algorithm geos like below:
int maximum_sum_so_far = 0
int curr_sum = 0
for (i=0;i < n; i++){
curr_sum += arr[i]
if curr_sum > maximum_sum_so_far:
maximum_sum_so_far = curr_sum
else if curr_sum <0:
    curr_sum = 0
